snippet.title: Into the Dead: Our Darkest Days - Gameplay Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Check out new gameplay of Into the Dead: Our Darkest Days, a side-scrolling survival game in a scorching post-apocalypse filled with the undead.

Into the Dead: Our Darkest Days is coming soon to PC. A demo will be available in October.

#IGN #Gaming #IntotheDead
